==============================================================================
Frankl-NonNatural-Cochain-Probe  mg-e1e2  (n=3)
==============================================================================

Testing non-F-natural IE cochain candidates on the 12 CE-shape
families at n=3.  Per mg-e466 each is RED for every F-natural
construction; this probe tests whether the structurally identified
escape (non-natural data d breaks F's symmetry) actually fires.

